                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="post-content">
                    <h4>How FreshShare changed my relationship with food waste</h4>
                    <p>I used to throw away so much produce before it could be used. After joining FreshShare, I've cut my food waste by 80% and saved over $200 monthly! Here's how my journey started...</p>
                </div>
                <div class="post-actions">
                    <div class="action-item liked">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                        <span>48 Likes</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="action-item">
                        <i class="far fa-comment"></i>
                        <span>23 Comments</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="action-item saved">
                        <i class="fas fa-bookmark"></i>
                        <span>Saved</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Regular Post -->
            <div class="forum-card">
                <div class="post-header">
                    <img src="/api/placeholder/100/100" alt="User Avatar" class="user-avatar">
                    <div class="post-user-info">
                        <h5>Michael Chen</h5>
                        <div class="post-meta">
                            <span><i class="far fa-clock me-1"></i> 2 hours ago</span>
                            <span class="category-badge">Tips & Tricks</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="post-content">
                    <h4>Best practices for storing vegetables</h4>
                    <p>I've experimented with different storage methods for keeping vegetables fresh longer. Here are my top 5 discoveries that have made a huge difference in extending the life of my produce...</p>
                </div>
                <div class="post-actions">
                    <div class="action-item">
                        <i class="far fa-heart"></i>
                        <span>24 Likes</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="action-item">
                        <i class="far fa-comment"></i>
                        <span>8 Comments</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="action-item">
                        <i class="far fa-bookmark"></i>
                        <span>Save</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Regular Post -->
            <div class="forum-card">
                <div class="post-header">
                    <img src="/api/placeholder/100/100" alt="User Avatar" class="user-avatar">
                    <div class="post-user-info">
                        <h5>Sarah Williams</h5>
                        <div class="post-meta">
                            <span><i class="far fa-clock me-1"></i> 6 hours ago</span>
                            <span class="category-badge">Questions</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
